name: Structvisualizer
tagline: Javafx app with animations for Collection and Set basic methods
body: # Struct Visualizer Struct Visualizer is an educational program written on JavaFX. Program designed to simplify learning process of Java/C++ collections. It's animating simple methods from Java Collections Framework and giving user the source code to have same results in his program. Implemented methods partly taken from Collection and Set interfaces in JSDK. Program can animate methods from such structures: ArrayList, Stack, HashMap, Set.
